<P>
   BUSH-BIO-VII (Undated) _ Feature on the 1988 presidential
campaign and George W. Bush's role in his father's successful race.
By Nicholas D. Kristof. Latest in a series looking at the career of
the Republican nominee. (The story has moved in ``p'' news file; a
