interview, which is available as a ``separate-buy'' _ the cost is
not prohibitive _ by contacting one of the New York Times Syndicate
sales representatives listed below.) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   METALLICA: STILL DANGEROUS AFTER ALL THESE YEARS
</P>
<P>
