for couples traveling together; Residential with a full-service
kitchen; Business with office area including printer, fax machine,
and separate modem line; and 474 Kidsuites with two bedrooms _ one
for adults, the other child-friendly _ along with games for the
kids. For grandparents traveling with grandchildren, the resort is
