   TRAVEL-COLLINS (Oberhofen, Austria) _ Hay that Stefan Feldbacher
pitchforks to the cows is so transportingly aromatic that you
imagine the beefy munchers ecstatically glazed on a bovine high. By
Bud Collins. 1600 words.
</P>
