idea that no life should go unexamined _ in front of a national
audience. On Wednesday night, ABC News presents the first episode
of ``Hopkins 24/7,'' a six-part documentary series that has
captured three months of life and death at Johns Hopkins Medical
Center in Baltimore. Reviewed by Julie Salamon.
</P>
