<P>
   With LABOR-DATA, text material from the graphic. With 15-inch
sidebars from six Cox papers on how certain jobs have changed in
the past century: LABOR, RAILROAD, LABOR-TEACHER, LABOR-NCR,
LABOR-RETIREE, LABOR-GROWER, LABOR-POULTRY. WITH PHOTOS.
