   BEATING-DEATH (Tacoma, Wash.) _ Cops arrest seven Tacoma youths,
aged 11, 12 and 13 and up to 19, in connection with a beating death
and a series of muggings. They have linked the kids to 9 attacks,
including the murder. Cops say the attacks were conducted ``for the
hell of it,'' with kids beating, stomping and using sticks against
their victims.
</P>
<P>
   By Jack Hopkins. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
