<P>
   FOOTBALL-PRAYER (Santa Fe, Texas) _ The leader of a group that
supports a prayer before public high school football games plans
for an ``army of prayer warriors'' to show up at Santa Fe High
School's first game to recite the Lord's Prayer. In June, the
Supreme Court ruled that the widespread practice of student-led
prayers over loudspeakers at games is unconstitutional. By KEVIN
MORAN.
</P>
