   TEXAS-DROUGHT (Dallas) _ For 59 days it hasn't rained in Dallas
and for 36 days the temperature has been over 100. And in the
western town of Throckmorton, officials are building a water supply
pipeline at a time when reserves are dwindling. By EVAN MOORE.
