   RIGHT SIDE:
</P>
<P>
   TIRE-RECALL (Detroit) _ Bridgestone/Firestone Inc. announced on
Tuesday evening that it had asked its dealers in Venezuela to
return unsold 15- and 16-inch light truck tires made there, but the
company rebuffed the Ford Motor Co.'s request for a recall of
identical tires already in use in Venezuela, Colombia and Ecuador.
By Keith Bradsher.
</P>
