   AT&AMP;T-EXCITE (Undated) _ AT&AMP;T says it has assume voting control
of Excite(at)Home earlier than expected and said 2000 earnings will
be 1 cent to 2 cents lower than forecast. The stock rises more than
3 percent in early trading. Also, shares of AT&AMP;T Latin America
being trading. By Simon Romero.
</P>
