Crisafulli peers through a gap in the tarp on the fence surrounding
the Arthur Ashe Tennis Center, Tuesday. Crisafulli was trying to
get a glimpse of Jason Stoltenberg playing Jan Siemerink in the
U.S. Open. For those tennis fans not lucky enough to have tickets
