do. (Ruth Fremson/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT22) NEW YORK -- Aug. 29, 2000 -- DLJ-CREDIT-SUISSE --
Donaldson, Lufkin &AMP; Jenrette shares surged more than 22 percent
Tuesday after it became clear the investment bank was in talks to
be sold to a larger rival, Credit Suisse First Boston. Allen Wheat,
